name: Do It (Yannolle)
description:
Explore the madness that happens when you're hungry, thirsty and alone...

We hope you enjoy the game we have created, all done from scratch, including audio, materials, assets and voices of our own, to make the game authentic in the spirit of Game Jams! 

Mia & David
